## A note on sources

Some records are seeded or verified from [MusicBrainz](https://musicbrainz.org),
whose core data is released under CC0 (public domain). CC0 data can be
incorporated here without conflict. Where a connection's evidence comes from a
third party (Apple Music credits, liner notes, etc.), that link is a *citation*
of the source, not a claim over the source's own content.

